							fileref="images/Screen_diff_testHardware_ADS13x.svg" format="SVG"
							width="80%"/>
					</imageobject>
				</mediaobject>
			</example>
			<para>The benefit of the flattened view is to have all the differences in a single
				picture:</para>
			<para>
				<itemizedlist>
